    <briefdescription>
<para>An RTIO context containing what can be viewed as a pair of queues. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A queue for submissions (available and in queue to be produced) as well as a queue of completions (available and ready to be consumed).</para>
<para>The rtio executor along with any objects implementing the <ref refid="structrtio__iodev" kindref="compound">rtio_iodev</ref> interface are the consumers of submissions and producers of completions.</para>
<para>No work is started until <ref refid="group__rtio_1gafee27c64a4a4989c4eb774addde8eb2e" kindref="member">rtio_submit()</ref> is called. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
